#: ../../mcp/reference/purchase.md:1
msgid "Purchase (`lu_mcp_purchase`)"
msgstr "Purchase (`lu_mcp_purchase`)"

#: ../../mcp/reference/purchase.md:3
msgid "**6 tools** for Odoo purchase orders and RFQs (Requests for Quotation)."
msgstr "Odoo 구매 주문 및 RFQ(견적 요청)를 위한 **6가지 도구**입니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/purchase.md:5
msgid "Requires: `lu_mcp_server`, Odoo `purchase` app."
msgstr "필수: `lu_mcp_server`, Odoo `purchase` 앱."

#: ../../mcp/reference/purchase.md:9
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "개요"

#: ../../mcp/reference/purchase.md:11
msgid ""
"These tools cover the purchase order lifecycle: search, read, create, "
"update, confirm, and log notes. RFQs in `draft` or `sent` state can be "
"edited; confirmed Purchase Orders (`purchase`) are locked."
msgstr ""
"이 도구들은 구매 주문 생명 주기를 다룹니다: 검색, 읽기, 생성, 업데이트, 확정, 메모 기록. "
"`draft` 또는 `sent` 상태의 RFQ는 편집 가능하고, 확정된 구매 주문(`purchase`)은 잠깁니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/purchase.md:15
msgid ""
"**Order states**: `draft` (RFQ), `sent` (RFQ Sent), `purchase` (Purchase "
"Order), `done` (Locked), `cancel` (Cancelled)."
msgstr ""
"**주문 상태**: `draft`(RFQ), `sent`(RFQ 발송), `purchase`(구매 주문), `done`(잠금), `cancel`(취소)."

